OL,3,CWoman prosecuted for second time after
OL,4,Ccausing community's rat problem.
OL,6,FA woman has been prosecuted for a
OL,7,Fsecond time after continuing to feed
OL,8,Fwildlife in the Amman Valley area.
OL,10,FShe was taken to court by Neath Port
OL,11,FTalbot Council's Environmental Health
OL,12,FTeam after her actions attracted
OL,13,Frodents and caused a significant
OL,14,Fpublic health risk.
OL,16,FA primary school in Tairgwaith, local
OL,17,Fbusinesses and residents reported a
OL,18,Flarge number of rats after the woman
OL,19,Ffailed to comply with a previous legal
OL,20,Fnotice that had been issued.
