OL,3,CWoman prosecuted for second time after
OL,4,Ccausing community's rat problem.
OL,6,FThe rodents began appearing after
OL,7,Flarge amounts of bird feed were left
OL,8,Fin her garden. She was also seen
OL,9,Fleaving meat on public land, which the
OL,10,Fcouncil said risked the safety of
OL,11,Flocal dogs and other animals.
OL,13,FDuring sentencing at Swansea
OL,14,FMagistrates Court, the woman was given
OL,15,Fa two-year Criminal Behaviour Order
OL,16,Fand a several restrictions to prevent
OL,17,Fher from feeding birds in public
OL,18,Fspaces.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
