CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781871073
OL,3,CWoman prosecuted for second time after
OL,4,Ccausing community's rat problem.
OL,6,FThe measures included being limited to
OL,7,Ftwo bird feeders to be used at any one
OL,8,Ftime, with each feeder only being
OL,9,Ffilled once a week. She was also
OL,10,Fordered to keep any food outside in
OL,11,Fsealed containers.
OL,13,FThe woman was ordered to pay a fine of
OL,14,F#1,500.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
