PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781871073
OL,3,CWoman prosecuted for second time after
OL,4,Ccausing community's rat problem.
OL,6,FCabinet Member for Nature, Tourism and
OL,7,FWellbeing, Cllr Cen Phillips said:
OL,8,F"Whilst feeding birds may be well
OL,9,Fintentioned, in this instance it
OL,10,Fresulted in a significant public
OL,11,Fhealth concern due to increased vermin
OL,12,Factivity affecting nearby homes, a
OL,13,Fschool and a community facility.
OL,15,F"The council's priority is always to
OL,16,Fwork with residents to resolve issues
OL,17,Finformally wherever possible. However,
OL,18,Fwhere there is a failure to comply
OL,19,Fwith legal requirements and the impact
OL,20,Fon the local area continues, we will
OL,21,Ftake appropriate action."
