OL,3,CWoman prosecuted for second time after
OL,4,Ccausing community's rat problem.
OL,6,FNeath Port Talbot Council are now
OL,7,Furging residents to consider the
OL,8,Fimpact their actions can have on the
OL,9,Fwider community.
